skdetail:
Flash Briefing Skill
Rated: Mature. This skill contains: dynamic content.
des:
In a world filled with counterfeit business experts and con artist success gurus, Andy Frisella is the real deal. A successful entrepreneur and bona fide millionaire, he’s also a “regular dude” who powered through years of frustration and failure in business to found six companies and build a 9-figure empire.

In this series, listen as Andy riffs, reasons, and rants his way through every topic relevant to success in business and life, from creating exceptional customer experience to maximizing your personal productivity. Vision, work ethic, culture, relationships, sales…it’s all here.

The MFCEO Kill Shots are not for the faint of heart or the easily offended; so if that’s you, you might want to pass. Just know you’ll be passing on information that will help dominate every aspect of your life.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
